    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Exact</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> ad XX Castoris </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Ex</abbr><ex>actum</ex></expan> ad X <expan><abbr>Cast</abbr><ex>oris</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Ex</abbr><ex>actum</ex></expan> V <expan><abbr>Ca</abbr><ex>storis</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Ex</abbr><ex>actum</ex></expan> III <expan><abbr>Ca</abbr><ex>storis</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="5" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Ex</abbr><ex>actum</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>Ca</abbr><ex>storis</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="6" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Ex</abbr><ex>actum</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>Ca</abbr><ex>storis</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="7" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Exa</abbr><ex>ctum</ex></expan> |(semis) <expan><abbr>Cas</abbr><ex>toris</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="8" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> |(triens) </ab></div><div n="9" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> |(quadrans) </ab></div><div n="10" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Ex</abbr><ex>actum</ex></expan> |(sextans) <expan><abbr>Ca</abbr><ex>storis</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="11" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> |(uncia)
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Satz von 11 bronzenen Kapselgewichten, die ineinandergestapelt werden können; möglicherweise komplett bis auf das Gewicht einer halben uncia. Maße beziehen sich auf das größte Gewicht. Inschriften eingraviert; die Einheiten uncia, sextans, quadrans und triens sind durch Punkte angegeben, in die Blei eingehämmert wurde. (B): Glaser; Weber - Pesditschek; AE 2001: Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
